&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Local Structure&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>README</title><link>http://localhost:1313/documents/hugo-docs-template/readme/</link><pubDate>Sat, 03 Jan 2026 10:55:17 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://localhost:1313/documents/hugo-docs-template/readme/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="hugo-documentation-site-deployment-automation"&gt;Hugo Documentation Site Deployment Automation&lt;a class="anchor" href="#hugo-documentation-site-deployment-automation"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;One-command deployment of secure Hugo documentation sites to AWS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This automation system creates a complete, production-ready documentation site with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;âœ… Hugo static site with hugo-book theme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;âœ… AWS S3 storage (completely private)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;âœ… CloudFront CDN with HTTPS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;âœ… Lambda@Edge password protection + URL rewriting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;âœ… GitHub repository with auto-deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;âœ… ~60-90 second deployment pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="quick-start"&gt;Quick Start&lt;a class="anchor" href="#quick-start"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-prerequisites"&gt;1. Prerequisites&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-prerequisites"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Install tools (macOS)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew install hugo awscli gh python3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Configure AWS&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;aws configure
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Enter: Access Key ID, Secret Key, Region, Output format&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Authenticate with GitHub&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;gh auth login
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Install Python dependencies&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip3 install boto3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="2-deploy-a-new-docs-site"&gt;2. Deploy a New Docs Site&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-deploy-a-new-docs-site"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
